{"tid":1909792,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【重口味】尼馬開P親密攬女 對方竟係有男朋友嘅32歲大媽","createTime":"2020-03-04T08:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T03:02:52.000Z","uid":217098,"like":9,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"889b681e0c0513f6515c83a51b3b2b0ae7a23c0c","tid":1909792,"uid":217098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:14:38.000Z","msg":"尼馬日前開「白色派對」賀自己28歲牛一，派對期間，這位巴西前鋒被影到與巴西女歌手瑪拉莎（Mara&iacute;sa）行為親密。<br />\n相關新聞：【堅轉會】歐洲之旅僅一年告終 昌子源重返日職投飛腳<br />\n派對期間，尼馬被影到與巴西女歌手瑪拉莎（Mara&iacute;sa）行為親密，尼馬攬住瑪拉莎咬耳仔，然後尼馬突然向前索吻，瑪拉莎表現都相當受落。不過，有指瑪拉莎是目前是戀愛中，男朋友是一位商人，而尼馬目前是單身。<br />\n32歲的巴西女歌手瑪拉莎是組合Maiara &amp; Maraisa的一員，有指他們正進行歐洲巡迴演出，所以能出席在巴黎舉行的派對<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20200204/OXJUI5UM3YKJTN2353D4MKEW2E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200204%2FOXJUI5UM3YKJTN2353D4MKEW2E%2F&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=f8c1a7ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200204%2FOXJUI5UM3YKJTN2353D4MKEW2E%2F&h=f4480793\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20200204/OXJUI5UM3YKJTN2353D4MKEW2E/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A54n2kQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA54n2kQ.png&h=d0f2fa1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YkGxE7H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYkGxE7H.png&h=80e5b888&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53e3f7839a6082812d51c92c3410c1d185cee99f","tid":1909792,"uid":217098,"like":71,"dislike":4,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:16:00.000Z","msg":"屁馬食慣後日妹，玩到冇野好玩了？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a3f4cb27bf8a19c0218c2bc21dba62907de4d4","tid":1909792,"uid":11059,"like":350,"dislike":3,"score":347,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:17:18.000Z","msg":"32